We are a team of experts having experience delivering High Quality Mobile Application & Website since 2011. We are a team of 78+ In-house Mobile App Developers, Website Developer & UI/UX Designers. We are providing service globally and have customers in more than 70 Countries. 

Technical Stacks Expertise in : 

✅ Mobile: Swift, Kotlin, ReactNative, Flutter.

✅ UI Design : Figma, XD, Photoshop,AI

description.content:
Welcome to our PRO GIG !


Our Dedicated and experienced Full Stack Developer can help & support you with the Following Technical Project related tasks;


  • New website development
  • Fixing, and resolving issues/bugs in existing websites
  • Web applications
  • Adding new features, enhancing new functionalities
  • Restful API, JSON API
  • API integrations
  • Payment gateways integrations - PayPal, Stripe, Omise, Pay tab, Paytm, Razorpay [Any payment gateway]
  • technically anything and everything that we know and can help you :-)


So, we have Smart, Elite or Pro developers who are experienced in major technologies like:


  • PHP/MySQL
  • Laravel /Node
  • MongoDB
  • Vuejs/ReactJs
  • Javascript, jquery
  • SQL/Database
  • HTML5,CSS3
  • Boostrap


Process :


  • Short intro call with Developer
  • Share Scope of work, SRS, Specs Detail Doc etc.
  • Place an Order


Please note that we are not providing any fixed cost or timeline for any existing projects fixing the issues/bugs under this gig.


IMPORTANT:


Before you place an order for this gig let us quickly discuss and will take it further.

For any kind of existing project task, we need to verify the working state of the web app, and set up the environment and code quality before working on it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work on Existing Code and Make Change ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we do work on Existing code, But Before placing an order we must need to verify code quality. If Code quality is ups to basic standards then we will able to work on it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is Experience of Developers who will work on Order
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We are a team of more than 80+ Inhouse Developers. Generally, All Developer who works on this order will be from 2 Years to 5 Years of experience.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you help me to setup entire team of of Developer ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we are a team of 70+ Inhouse Developers. We can help you to set up the entire scrum team and they can work on your product.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How we can track hours developers are working ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Our developer will send you daily work reports. Also, you can track developers' hours via time-tracking software like Hubstaff.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide any free trial to check developers quality of work ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes For the monthly package, we provide 2 days of a free trial.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you sign NDA for project idea confidentiality ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, We are happy to sign NDA for any project.

reviews.comment:
iCoderz did a satisfactory job on the broad outlines of my project, which was not easy to explain and understand in its entirety due to its concept and the way it was presented.
We exceeded the delivery deadline on 2 occasions because we had to readjust certain points, but we were able to find alternatives and modifications that enabled us to achieve a coherent result.
In spite of everything, the team listened to us and we had regular exchanges throughout the creation of the wireframe and the design.
The next stage will be development, which will be just as complex and ambitious. Thank you
Icoderz is a serious and reliable software-factory, great working with Mitul and Ankit, professional and efficient people. Will keep working together.
Happy with the professionalism and expertise of ICoderz. They went beyond the scope of the project and made improvements to our suggested designs.
Good work, they adapt to feedback and requirements. Recommended.

Icoderz is amazing! 🤩 I can be difficult to work with sometimes because I make constant changes and create new ideas lol But Icoderz was professional and friendly and made sure they delivered exactly what I requested every time. They went above what my vision was and brought it to a better level due to their experience. I highly recommend them, seriously, they are the best at what they do! If you're looking for a team to help you, look no further.
